# Movie SQL Analysis

## Project Overview
This project analyzes a movie dataset using PostgreSQL. It demonstrates SQL concepts including data retrieval, aggregation, ranking functions, Common Table Expressions (CTEs), and views.

## Tools Used
- PostgreSQL
- SQL
- GitHub

## Features
- Movie rating analysis
- Revenue analysis
- Genre performance analysis
- Director performance analysis
- Window functions (RANK, DENSE_RANK, ROW_NUMBER)
- CTEs and Views

## Skills Demonstrated
- SELECT Statements
- GROUP BY
- ORDER BY
- Aggregate Functions
- Window Functions
- CTEs
- Database Design

## Files
- movie_database_project.sql : Complete SQL script for the project
